import React, { useEffect } from 'react' import group from '../img/MyGroup.jpg' import SideBar from '../Components/SideBar' import '../CSS/BlogPage.css' import lang from '../lang' function Blog() {useEffect(() => { const select = document.querySelector('select') const allLang = ['en', 'ru'] select.addEventListener('change', changeURLLanguage) function changeURLLanguage() { let lang = select.value window.location.href = window.location.pathname + '#' + lang window.location.reload() changeLanguage() // Add this line to call the changeLanguage function after page reload } function changeLanguage() { let hash = window.location.hash hash = hash.substring(1) console.log(hash) if (!allLang.includes(hash)) { window.location.href = window.location.pathname + '#ru' window.location.reload() } select.value = hash for (let key in lang) { const element = document.querySelector('.lng-' + key) if (element) { element.innerHTML = lang[key][hash] } } } changeLanguage() // Call the function to check the initial language on page load }, []) return (
